<plot>11-year-old Ian loves to play video games. Especially violent ones. That all changes, however, when he plays Hot Wired 3, an extremely graphic and sexually explicit video game that's intended for mature audiences. Hot Wired 3 sucks Ian into a virtual world of whores, drugs and colorful thugs, and where murder and mayhem are all too real. Fearing for his life, Ian desperately tries to navigate the game and avoid getting killed. But before he can do that he must figure out how to make it to the next level.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?209259</url></doc>
